# Nodara Network Dashboard - Component Specifications

## Layout Components

### MainLayout
- **Description**: Root layout component that provides the base structure for the dashboard
- **Features**:
  - Responsive container
  - Navigation structure
  - Theme provider integration
  - Authentication wrapper

### Navbar
- **Description**: Top navigation bar with key controls and user information
- **Features**:
  - Wallet connection button
  - User profile menu
  - Navigation links
  - Network status indicator
  - Theme toggle

### Sidebar
- **Description**: Main navigation sidebar with categorized menu items
- **Features**:
  - Collapsible menu structure
  - Active route highlighting
  - Icon + text navigation items
  - Quick access shortcuts

## Service Marketplace Components

### ServiceCatalog
- **Description**: Grid display of available services
- **Features**:
  - Service cards
  - Filter controls
  - Search functionality
  - Sorting options
  - Pagination

### ServiceCard
- **Description**: Individual service display component
- **Features**:
  - Service icon/image
  - Price display
  - Quick action buttons
  - Status indicator
  - Rating display

### ServiceDetailModal
- **Description**: Detailed view of a selected service
- **Features**:
  - Complete service information
  - Provider details
  - Pricing breakdown
  - Booking interface
  - Historical metrics

### ServiceRequestForm
- **Description**: Form for configuring and requesting services
- **Features**:
  - Service parameters
  - Price calculator
  - SLA options
  - Payment method selection
  - Confirmation flow

## Device Map Components

### GlobalMap
- **Description**: Interactive map showing node distribution
- **Features**:
