  - Interactive tooltips
  - Zoom controls

### MapFilters
- **Description**: Control panel for map visualization
- **Features**:
  - Service type filters
  - Location filters
  - Status filters
  - Custom search
  - Filter combinations

### NodeMarker
- **Description**: Individual node representation on map
- **Features**:
  - Status indicator
  - Quick info tooltip
  - Click interaction
  - Custom icons by type
  - Animation states

